    "created_at": "2016-01-26T14:26:36Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-01-26T14:27:23Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "In my opinion, `MaximumSpeed` should be slightly refactored to be `MaximumAddedSpeed`, and internally max speed should then be `MinimumSpeed` + `MaximumAddedSpeed`. This would have several advantages, \n1) by default, the difference between minimum and maximum speed would be the same for all missiles,\n2) the risk of modders accidentally setting a `MinimumSpeed` higher than `MaximumSpeed` would disappear,\n3) we could set the internal default of `MaximumAddedSpeed` to `0`, meaning min speed = max speed, which is a much saner default for our shipping mods.\n\nEdit: I'm not convinced of the name `MaximumAddedSpeed`, feel free to make a better suggestion.\n"
  },
